{{作品名稱|name=''Loving''|hk=相愛很難|tw=愛侶|cn=爱恋}}是一部2016年[[英國|英國]]和[[美國|美國]]合拍的[[時代劇|時代]][[傳記片|傳記]][[劇情片|劇情片]]，電影的靈感源自2011年由Nancy Buirski執導的紀錄片《漫長回家路：一個愛情故事》（{{lang|en|''The Loving Story''}}），電影根據發生於1967年[[美國最高法院|美國最高法院]]（[[厄尔·沃伦|沃伦法院]]）對《{{le|洛文夫婦控訴維吉尼亞州案|Loving v. Virginia}}》的裁決<ref>{{Cite web|title=Loving v. Virginia|url=https://www.oyez.org/cases/1966/395|accessdate=2019-09-26|author=|date=|format=|work=|publisher=Oyez|language=en|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511192557/https://www.oyez.org/cases/1966/395|dead-url=no}}</ref>，當中涉及維吉尼亞州禁止種族間婚姻的法律<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-a-fest-few-lows-896614|title=Cannes: A Fest of Few Lows, But Only One Real High|last=McCarthy|first=Todd|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2016-05-23|accessdate=2017-01-02|archive-date=2017-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112201841/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-a-fest-few-lows-896614|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/article/2016/09/13/ruth-negga-joel-edgerton-loving-tiff/|title=TIFF 2016: Loving stars Ruth Negga, Joel Edgerton on film's reluctant heroes|last=Coggan|first=Devan|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-09-13|accessdate=2017-01-02|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106102041/http://ew.com/article/2016/09/13/ruth-negga-joel-edgerton-loving-tiff/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/midnight-special-jeff-nichols-aquaman-warner-bros-the-screening-room-1201723429/|title=‘Midnight Special’ Director Jeff Nichols On Final Cut, ‘Aquaman’ & Why HDTV Evolution Is More Important Than The Screening Room|last=D'Alessandro|first=Anthony|work=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|date=2016-03-20|accessdate=2017-01-02|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106011036/http://deadline.com/2016/03/midnight-special-jeff-nichols-aquaman-warner-bros-the-screening-room-1201723429/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並隨著《洛文夫婦控訴維吉尼亞州案》的發展而拍攝<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/article/2015/05/08/loving-supreme-court-case-jeff-nichols/|title=Landmark Loving Supreme Court Case to be made into a film|last=McGovern|first=Joe|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-05-08|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106015144/http://ew.com/article/2015/05/08/loving-supreme-court-case-jeff-nichols/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/loving-joel-edgerton-and-ruth-negga-lead-jeff-nichols-next-film/|title=Joel Edgerton and Ruth Negga to Lead MUD Director Jeff Nichols’ LOVING|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|work=[[Collider.com|Collider.com]]|date=2016-05-08|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106010747/http://collider.com/loving-joel-edgerton-and-ruth-negga-lead-jeff-nichols-next-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.charlotteobserver.com/entertainment/ent-columns-blogs/lawrence-toppman/article116355443.html|title=Loving was their name, loving was their crime|last=Toppman|first=Lawrence|work=[[The_Charlotte_Observer|The Charlotte Observer]]|date=2016-11-21|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106011238/http://www.charlotteobserver.com/entertainment/ent-columns-blogs/lawrence-toppman/article116355443.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

電影由[[傑夫·尼可拉斯|傑夫·尼可拉斯]]執導及編劇<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/article/2015/05/08/loving-supreme-court-case-jeff-nichols/|title=Landmark Loving Supreme Court Case to be made into a film|last=McGovern|first=Joe|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2015-05-08|accessdate=2017-01-02|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106015144/http://ew.com/article/2015/05/08/loving-supreme-court-case-jeff-nichols/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由[[喬爾·埃哲頓|喬爾·埃哲頓]]及[[露絲·奈嘉|露絲·奈嘉]]主演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2015/05/ruth-negga-and-joel-edgerton-will-star-in-adaptation-of-the-loving-story-landmark-civil-rights-anti-miscegenation-case-154417/|title=Ruth Negga and Joel Edgerton Will Star in Adaptation of ‘The Loving Story’ – Landmark Civil Rights Anti-Miscegenation Case|last=A. Obenson|first=Tambay|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=2015-05-08|accessdate=2017-01-02|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106010950/http://www.indiewire.com/2015/05/ruth-negga-and-joel-edgerton-will-star-in-adaptation-of-the-loving-story-landmark-civil-rights-anti-miscegenation-case-154417/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[馬頓·索柯斯|馬頓·索柯斯]]、{{link-en|尼克·克羅爾|Nick Kroll}}及[[麥可·夏儂|麥可·夏儂]]作為配角<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2015/09/michael-shannon-reteams-with-jeff-nichols-for-loving-259432/|title=Michael Shannon Reteams With Jeff Nichols For ‘Loving’|last=Jagernauth|first=Kevin|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=2015-09-22|accessdate=2017-01-02|archive-date=2017-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170106012201/http://www.indiewire.com/2015/09/michael-shannon-reteams-with-jeff-nichols-for-loving-259432/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。主要攝影於[[維珍尼亞州|維珍尼亞州]][[里士满_(维吉尼亚州)|列治文]]取景，[[國王與王后縣_(維吉尼亞州)|國王與王后縣]]、[[加羅林縣_(維吉尼亞州)|加羅林縣]]等也有取景，於2015年9月16日開始，並於11月19日結束。

電影於2016年5月16日在[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上首映並入選競爭[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]<ref name="IW">{{cite web |url=http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |title=2016 Cannes Film Festival Announces Lineup |accessdate=2016-04-14 |work=IndieWire |archive-date=2016-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505030458/http://www.indiewire.com/article/cannes-live-stream-2016-film-festival-lineup-list |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="VarCannes">{{cite web |url=http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |title=Cannes 2016: Film Festival Unveils Official Selection Lineup |accessdate=2016-04-14 |work=Variety |archive-date=2016-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160423225526/http://variety.com/2016/film/festivals/cannes-film-festival-official-selection-lineup-2016-1201753269/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並由[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]定於2016年11月4日在美國作[[有限上映|有限上映]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gq.com/story/midnight-special-jeff-nichols|title=The Shot Caller Q+A: Midnight Special Director Jeff Nichols|last=Baron|first=Zac|work=[[GQ|GQ]]|date=2016-03-25|accessdate=2016-12-31|archive-date=2017-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170318025509/http://www.gq.com/story/midnight-special-jeff-nichols|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並於2016年11月11日廣泛上映<ref name="RELEASE"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://ew.com/article/2016/03/15/loving-joel-edgerton-ruth-negga-release-date/|title='Loving' starring Joel Edgerton, Ruth Negga gets November release date|last=Robinson|first=Will|work=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2016-03-15|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2017-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118081135/http://ew.com/article/2016/03/15/loving-joel-edgerton-ruth-negga-release-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiewire.com/2016/03/focus-features-sets-release-date-for-new-jeff-nichols-film-loving-58007/|title=Focus Features Sets Release Date For New Jeff Nichols Film ‘Loving’|last=Santos|first=Nix|work=[[Indiewire|Indiewire]]|date=2016-03-15|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113160506/http://www.indiewire.com/2016/03/focus-features-sets-release-date-for-new-jeff-nichols-film-loving-58007/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影獲得積極的評價，被幾個媒體稱為2016年最佳電影之一<ref name="Metacritic">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-list-the-top-10-movies-of-2016|title=Best of 2016: Film Critic Top Ten Lists|last=Dietz|first=Jason|work=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|date=2016-12-05|accessdate=2016-12-13|archive-date=2016-12-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161206002013/http://www.metacritic.com/feature/film-critics-list-the-top-10-movies-of-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影被提名到不同的獎項，包括[[金球獎|金球獎]]最佳男主角，以及[[金球獎|金球獎]]和[[奧斯卡獎|奧斯卡獎]]的最佳女主角<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/12/the-golden-globes-favor-la-la-land-moonlight-and-more/510353/|title=La La Land and Moonlight See Golden Globes Love|last=Sims|first=David|work=[[The_Atlantic|The Atlantic]]|date=2016-12-12|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2017-01-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170113151340/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2016/12/the-golden-globes-favor-la-la-land-moonlight-and-more/510353/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/12/golden-globe-nominations-2017-full-list|title=2017 Golden Globes Nominations: The Full List|last=Vanity Fair Editors|first=|work=[[Vanity_Fair_(magazine)|Vanity Fair]]|date=2016-12-12|accessdate=2016-12-30|archive-date=2016-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161215122348/http://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2016/12/golden-globe-nominations-2017-full-list|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==劇情==
故事敘述一名白人男性和黑人女性因相愛而結婚，兩人為此違反了[[反異族通婚法|反異族通婚法]]而遭到了拘捕，並於1958年在[[維吉尼亞州|維吉尼亞州]]被判获罪，缓刑驱逐出州并流放至[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|華盛頓]]。兩人提起了一連串的訴訟，以申訴法律禁止[[異族通婚|異族通婚]]是一種違憲的不公行為，并受到[[美国公民自由协会|美国公民自由协会]]（ACLU）的帮助和支持。

