==發行==
2016年2月，[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]獲得了其在美國的發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/02/loving-joel-edgerton-ruth-negga-michael-shannon-focus-features-interracial-civil-rights-richard-and-mildred-loving-berlin-1201702174/|title=Focus Features Makes Big Berlin Deal; $9 Million For Interracial Marriage Drama ‘Loving’|first1=Mike|last1=Fleming Jr.|first2=Ali|last2=Jafaar|date=2016-02-13|accessdate=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160516155511/http://deadline.com/2016/02/loving-joel-edgerton-ruth-negga-michael-shannon-focus-features-interracial-civil-rights-richard-and-mildred-loving-berlin-1201702174/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影最先於2016年5月16日在[[第69屆坎城影展|第69屆坎城影展]]上入選競爭[[金棕櫚獎|金棕櫚獎]]<ref name="IW"/><ref name="VarCannes"/>。本片定於2016年11月4日在美國上映<ref name="RELEASE">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/03/focus-features-dates-jeff-nichols-loving-1201721001/|title=Focus Features Dates Jeff Nichols’ ‘Loving’|first=Anthony D'|last=Alessandro|date=2016-03-15|accessdate=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521130313/http://deadline.com/2016/03/focus-features-dates-jeff-nichols-loving-1201721001/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==反響==
影片獲得了正面好評。[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]新鮮度高達93%，平均得分7.3／10<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771439525/|title=Loving (2016)|website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]]|accessdate=2016-05-17|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520031910/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/771439525/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影在坎城影展上映後，獲得了全場起立鼓掌認同<ref>{{cite news|title=Cannes: Interracial love story 'Loving' is first awards season contender|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/05/16/interracial-love-story-loving-first-awards-season-contender/84435138/|accessdate=2016-05-17|work=USA TODAY|date=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521074940/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2016/05/16/interracial-love-story-loving-first-awards-season-contender/84435138/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》<ref name="The Hollywood Reporter 16 May 2016">{{cite news|last1=Kilday|first1=Gregg|title=Cannes Drama 'Loving' Shows Oscar Potential|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-drama-loving-shows-oscar-894327|accessdate=2016-05-17|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2016-05-16|archive-date=2016-05-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160517093910/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/cannes-drama-loving-shows-oscar-894327|dead-url=no}}</ref>、《[[人物_(雜誌)|人物]]》<ref>{{cite news|title=The Real Story of Richard and Mildred Loving – the Interracial Couple Who Fought for Their Right to Wed and Inspired the Cannes Film Already Earning Oscar Buzz|url=http://www.people.com/article/richard-mildred-loving-real-story-film-supreme-court-fight|accessdate=2016-05-17|work=[[People_(magazine)|People]]|archive-date=2016-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160518151024/http://www.people.com/article/richard-mildred-loving-real-story-film-supreme-court-fight|dead-url=no}}</ref>和《[[Essence_(雜誌)|Essence]]》<ref>{{cite news|last1=Akindele|first1=Toni|title=Cannes Interracial Marriage Drama ‘Loving’ is an Oscar Contender|url=http://www.essence.com/2016/05/17/cannes-interracial-marriage-drama-loving-oscar-contender|accessdate=2016-05-17|work=[[Essence_(magazine)|Essence]]|date=2016-05-17|archive-date=2016-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160520235722/http://www.essence.com/2016/05/17/cannes-interracial-marriage-drama-loving-oscar-contender|dead-url=no}}</ref>等多家媒體都給予了肯定的評價，並認定電影有資格競爭[[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]。多數影評人稱讚其敘事和不灑狗血的作風，以及喬爾·埃哲頓與露絲·奈嘉的精采演出。

